
{{alias}}( z )
    Returns the real and imaginary components of a complex number.

    Parameters
    ----------
    z: Complex
        Complex number.

    Returns
    -------
    out: Float64Array|Float32Array
        Array containing the real and imaginary components, respectively.

    Examples
    --------
    > var z = new {{alias:@stdlib/types/complex/complex128}}( 5.0, 3.0 );
    > var out = {{alias}}( z )
    <Float64Array>[ 5.0, 3.0 ]
